{"tid":1758240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議17區區議會聯合調查今屆大量種票賄選問題","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T14:01:44.000Z","uid":321374,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2271a9d87435fd5e274bf5a0a10f451d9c06916e","tid":1758240,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:35:08.000Z","msg":"千山萬水走到黎呢步<br />\n我知黎緊既日子會有大量既野需要做<br />\n既然攞到17區主導權<br />\n我認為其中一項重要既事<br />\n就係調查大規模種票同賄選<br />\n因為下年立法會選舉一定會種得更過份<br />\n<br />\n首先召選舉事務處同廉政公署黎照肺<br />\n果D信有曬地址同名<br />\n一對返申請人既轉地址申請表格<br />\n跟本就冇得走<br />\n我諗果度應該拉到幾千人<br />\n而且最好拉到代佢哋申請改地址既人同幕後黑手就更好<br />\n阿公阿婆到時實會話乜都唔知<br />\n既然唔知就要佢哋篤出邊個幫佢哋做<br />\n最重要係迫選舉事務處制訂防止種票既方案<br />\n例如加強認證方法，由其已經有呢批無此人信<br />\n可以整個懷疑種票名單，<br />\n佢哋下次再申請轉地址就可以方便查證<br />\n而且仲可以分析種票係來自邊一區<br />\n<br />\n今次贏純粹好彩，政府犯錯攻打大學<br />\n對方竟然動員到120萬鐵票<br />\n出年立法會選舉冇理由要手足黎多次死守校園<br />\n而且建制派都話個選舉唔公平<br />\n我相信佢哋唔會反對調查的<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmAXkJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmAXkJg.jpg&h=7434aafd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLcCkLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLcCkLH.jpg&h=56ff0b79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eefc2293626ea73407bfb63ab6549e69f72108f3","tid":1758240,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44f651519f5bcf459d7ab4d9103421716aa93c0c","tid":1758240,"uid":269481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"支持，一定要查到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a92b28955a16782cadb025c74483f321cc90c9","tid":1758240,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"唔可以比種票繼續"},{"pid":"eb603363ed8f8e49d537b99a1543cda936944bad","tid":1758240,"uid":296369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:55:27.000Z","msg":"支持支持！<br />\n將所拍到影到交比議員，舉部去ICAC, 公告於國際，比全世界知道中共不斷破壞香港法治及選舉！ <br />\n其後要商討點防止及制止......ICAC 應該要查埋中聯辦呢啲成日搞破壞嘅機構.......<br />\n據聞種票已經有好幾十萬，情況嚴重....."},{"pid":"6b41d59965c1008e9e3c85254b920dcaf513d0be","tid":1758240,"uid":288523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b827d97ba9e59c96c903742e2b1b1ba6e38ccc1","tid":1758240,"uid":276219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"啱呀 藍絲都有話泛民種票<br />\n咁調查種票一定係黃藍共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57272fa4eed0275c5f1123932ad0d4a4ce57aef5","tid":1758240,"uid":210396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd439dff2a85c1d5c65ac52489fbcdce50f3760","tid":1758240,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1495303f7dce75b567adf2cf5ce15f7d9c2d0531","tid":1758240,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"32ae503ae0ef145759fdf15a2152242321fa8ce6","tid":1758240,"uid":271807,"like":0,"di